RPM Spec files for building correct Oracle JVM RPM packages based on jpackage spec 
files. 
For building no-src rpm use NoSource option in spec file.

1. Download JDK (.bin, not the rpm package) from oracle web site into SOURCES directory
2. Download desired spec file 
3. Download *xsl from SOURCES and place them into local SOURCES directory
4. Rebuild with 
   rpmbuild -bb SPECS/java-1.6.0-sun-RELEASE.spec
